attributes.description: The Toughest 4-Letter Word on Wheels - JEEP.  This 2015 Jeep Cherokee 3.2 Limited A/T is the most comfortable ride with supreme off-road abilities and great space in the inside. Supporting great features such as rearview camera, front and rear parking sensors, lane departure warning, lane keep assist, rain-sensing windshield wipers, blind spot monitoring, rear cross traffic alert, forward collision warning, and automatic emergency braking. The Cherokee performs just as well on the daily commute as it does tackling trails. With comfortable leather seats, bluetooth, USB port, an 8.4-inch touch screen, Radio, navigation, proximity key entry, push-button start, and remote start. Also known to have great safety features such as stability control, front-impact airbags,side impact airbags,overhead airbags,knee airbags and anti-whiplash., With a full Dekra roadworthy and condition report, this is a vehicle that must be test driven to appreciate it's luxury. Please note that the price does not include dealership fees and smash and grab.
